      'ATC gap = &pound;3.80 &minus; &pound;3.20 = <strong>&pound;0.60 per cup above minimum</strong>',
      'Daily cost of excess capacity = &pound;0.60 &times; 300 = &pound;180',
      'The firm is productively inefficient: ATC (&pound;3.80) &gt; min ATC (&pound;3.20)'
